-- LuaTimer installation

   1. Edit 'Makefile' and  set LUAINC with the path for your Lua 5.1 headers.
      Under Mac OS X, also set the MACOSX_VERSION according your system.

   2. Use the command 'make' and the target system:
         make linux
      or
         make bsd
      or
         make macosx
 
   3. Copy the library 'src/luatimer.so' to some place in your LUA_CPATH.
